data.title: When was Ollie Bond killed?
data.meta_description: Answers is the place to go to get the answers you need and to ask the questions you want
data.text:
What animated TV series contains the quote Don't you have an umbrella Ollie and how did Ollie answer when asked Where is it?

From Family Guy:[Live hurricane report]Tom Tucker: And now to Ollie Williams, with our live hurricane report. Ollie?Ollie Williams: It's rainin' sideways!Tom Tucker: Don't you have an umbrella, Ollie?Ollie Williams: Had one!Tom Tucker: Where is it?Ollie Williams: Inside-out, five miles away!Tom Tucker: Can we get you anything, Ollie?Ollie Williams: Bring me some soup!Tom Tucker: What kind?Ollie Williams: Chunky!

Who killed James Bond?

No one has and no one will. James Bond will live on even if the dierectors have finsihed all the books they wil just have to impervise!

Puppet named Ollie?

Years ago, there was a children's show on television called "Kukla, Fran and Ollie" in which Kukla and Ollie were the puppets and Fran was the puppeteer. I thought I was too grown up to watch the show so I don't remember many specifics. You might want to do a web search on "Kukla, Fran and Ollie" for details.
